  (text "OUTPUT DISCONNECT: back-to-back NFETs, 2 parallel per direction (30A: ~2.3W\nspread over 4 packages). LTC7004 charge-pump driver, static switching only.\nOVP: VOUT_INT x 20/235 vs TL431B 2.495V -> trips 29.35V. The squeeze is real:\nceiling 28.4 < trip 29.4 < bus 30V, hence 0.1% divider + 0.5% reference\n(a 3V3-LDO-derived reference would wander past the bus voltage; docs/08 s.8)."
    (at 219.71 175.26 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)))
    (uuid 95ea5330-1472-4e42-84c2-62f7e26ccbcf)
  )

